{
  "texts": [
    "Despite these conceptual limitations, we are confident that our research makes a substantial conceptual and theoretical contribution by setting the framework for rigorously understanding the notion of sustainable AI in the public sector, and we thus do not feel that these are incompatible.",
    "Research would focus on the public sector, specifically on the problems and opportunities presented by using AI there.",
    "The study's overarching goal is to learn how to use artificial intelligence best to spur innovation in the public sector.",
    "It will also examine the obstacles and possibilities for improving government service delivery.Fig. 1 A1Fig.1A Conceptual Framework of AI Use in Government Services Using Organisational Theory[66] Fig.",
    "22Fig.2TIS Relation Structure[64]"
